 Displays a special popup when a player enters the map. See script command "specialpopup" for details on different popup types.
 
 ---------------------------------------
+
+---------------------------------------
+
+*friendly_fire
+
+Allows offensive skills to target allied party/guild members on this map.
+Normal alliance targeting is unchanged on maps without this mapflag.
+
+Example:
+
+prontera	mapflag	friendly_fire
+
+---------------------------------------
